00:03.740 --> 00:06.270
So, since your mom used
to handle the holidays,

00:06.280 --> 00:08.170
I thought we should
talk about a game plan

00:08.180 --> 00:10.339
for Thanksgiving and Christmas.

00:10.340 --> 00:12.680
Oh, I say we follow the
Conner tradition...

00:12.700 --> 00:14.176
spend every dime we have on Halloween,

00:14.200 --> 00:15.780
and then we have nothing
to be thankful for

00:15.800 --> 00:16.850
or buy gifts with.

00:19.260 --> 00:20.500
Hi, Mom. Hi, Aunt Jackie.

00:20.520 --> 00:22.340
- Hi.
- Hey. How was school?

00:22.360 --> 00:24.520
Good. We're learning about democracy.

00:24.560 --> 00:27.060
Oh, it's a class in ancient history, eh?

00:28.480 --> 00:30.530
We're doing projects about the election.

00:30.540 --> 00:31.820
I'm gonna take a poll at the mall

00:31.840 --> 00:33.140
to see how people voted.

00:33.180 --> 00:34.680
Oh, good, my 11-year-old

00:34.710 --> 00:36.160
approaching strangers at the mall.

00:36.170 --> 00:37.170
Why don't we double down and just

00:37.180 --> 00:38.840
have you hitchhike there?

00:39.880 --> 00:41.740
No, you're taking me.

00:41.750 --> 00:43.100
Oh, I-I-I can't.

00:43.120 --> 00:44.130
I have to work that day.

00:44.140 --> 00:45.780
I didn't tell you what day it was.

00:46.690 --> 00:48.420
Oh, you didn't?

00:48.480 --> 00:49.719
Well, let's not get bogged down

00:49.720 --> 00:50.850
in he said, she said.

00:52.090 --> 00:53.450
All right, what day is it?

00:53.460 --> 00:54.890
- Saturday.
- How about that?

00:54.920 --> 00:56.150
I actually have to work that day.

00:56.160 --> 00:59.300
Well, I'm free on Saturday.
I'd love to help.

00:59.320 --> 01:01.170
I think it's great that
you're hungry to learn

01:01.220 --> 01:03.180
about how democracy is supposed to work,

01:03.200 --> 01:04.860
'cause it's up to you young people

01:04.870 --> 01:07.100
to snatch it back from special interests

01:07.110 --> 01:10.330
and breathe new life into
this noble experiment

01:10.360 --> 01:12.440
that we call America.

01:13.480 --> 01:16.400
Guys, you got to see this.

