17:06.770 --> 17:07.960
Oh, the preacher comes out later.

17:07.970 --> 17:09.630
That's the deaconess.

17:09.640 --> 17:11.220
Oh, so you mean like an M.C.?

17:11.260 --> 17:13.739
Oh. Oh. I'm learning so much.

17:13.740 --> 17:16.200
That's the deaconess.
Preacher comes out later.

17:16.250 --> 17:18.240
That's the deaconess.
